videos.description: Ashton Hagans loses his defender at the top of the arc with a nifty behind-the-back move and then races to the rim for a powerful, posterizing slam vs. Texas A&M.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kentucky's Hagans rises up for a big poster slam) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Kentucky's Hagans rises up for a big poster slam

videos.description: Texas A&M's Josh Nebo pushes his way to the hoop before rising up for a powerful slam vs. Kentucky and then lets Nick Richards hear it in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Aggies' Nebo jams and talks trash on his way downcourt) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Aggies' Nebo jams and talks trash on his way downcourt

videos.description: Immanuel Quickley helps Kentucky out to a hot start vs. Texas A&M, scoring 16 points in the first half including four 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Quickley powers Wildcats with 16 1st-half points

videos.description: Josh Nebo hauls in a deep pass from Savion Flagg and throws it down with authority vs. Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Nebo flushes home an Aggies alley-oop) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Nebo flushes home an Aggies alley-oop

videos.description: Immanuel Quickley beats the shot clock with an impressive jumper late in the second half of Kentucky's win vs. Texas A&M.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Quickley splits a pair of defenders for clutch jumper) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Quickley splits a pair of defenders for clutch jumper

videos.description: Coach John Calipari details Immanuel Quickley's vast improvement on defense and just how proud he is of the 20-year-old guard's career-high, 30-point game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Calipari, Quickley talk Kentucky's defense, Quickley's 30-point game) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Calipari, Quickley talk Kentucky's defense, Quickley's 30-point game

videos.description: Texas A&M coach Buzz Williams experiences a variety of emotions on the sideline during the Aggies' loss to Kentucky, even taking off multiple layers of clothing throughout.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Buzz sweats out all his emotions on the sideline) 2020/2/25 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Buzz sweats out all his emotions on the sideline
